<h2 id="3rd-gitkraken">3rd. <a href="https://www.gitkraken.com/">GitKraken</a></h2>

<p>Surely this is the dearest customer of the guys. It is also available for Linux, macOS and Windows.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/git/gitkraken.jpg" alt="Top 5 Best Git Clients for Linux, Mac and Windows" /></p>

<p>To install on Linux, besides the possibility that you can download <a href="https://www.gitkraken.com/download">tar.gz</a>, <a href="https://www.gitkraken.com/download">.deb</a> or <a href="https://www.gitkraken.com/download">.rpm</a>, you can also install via <a href="https://snapcraft.io/gitkraken">Snap</a>:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>snap <span class="nb">install </span>gitkraken</code></pre></figure>

<p>For Windows and macOS, download directly from the page: <a href="https://www.gitkraken.com/download">https://www.gitkraken.com/download</a></p>

